						<p class="mt-3 text-base leading-8 text-secondary">Expanded possession is not automatically equal parenting time. Parents comparing it with a <a href="/50-50-custody-schedule/" class="text-accent underline decoration-line underline-offset-4 hover:text-primary">50/50 custody schedule</a> should calculate overnights, commute time, school responsibilities, and how the child handles transitions. The best schedule is the one the family can follow consistently.</p>
