						<p class="mt-3 text-base leading-8 text-secondary">A downloadable Texas parenting plan PDF is useful because it gives parents a structured starting point. The problem is that a static PDF does not show whether the schedule actually works on real dates. It cannot automatically generate calendars, calculate parenting time, update holidays, or show how summer possession changes the annual split.</p>
